{"data":[{"date":"09:44 29/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n V-League b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/13/tai-em-bat-ngo-ra-di-sau-thanh-tich-te-hai-cua-sai-gon-fc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u2018t\u1ee5t d\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng phanh\u2019 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean BXH, HLV T\u00e0i Em m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m<br>\r\n</span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng s\u1ed1c n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t th\u1eadt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL v\u00e0 SLNA v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ra \u0111i sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/13/tai-em-bat-ngo-ra-di-sau-thanh-tich-te-hai-cua-sai-gon-fc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 28/6, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi CLB. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cCLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft n\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f2n non ngh\u1ec1 \u1edf V-League. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chuy\u1ec7n chia tay ngay sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 gi\u1edd v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 r\u1ed3i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u1ea3 quan trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec1 ra. Xin ch\u00fac anh em nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n theo d\u00f5i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh em trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Tu\u1ea5n Phong \u0111\u00e3 thay m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi: \u201cAnh em ai c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00ec sao ra n\u00f4ng n\u1ed7i n\u00e0y. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00ec m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra \u0111i. S\u00e0i G\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i Em l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m, s\u1ed1ng h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed3ng, vui v\u1ebb n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng anh em trong \u0111\u1ed9i. CLB n\u00e0y v\u1ed1n r\u1ea5t l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e0i Em c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n th\u1ee9 hai ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 HLV Marian Mihail c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay FLC Thanh H\u00f3a sau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t c\u1ee7a\u00a0\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-325-189774.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-slna-32-sai-gon-vong-16-vleague-2018-325-189774.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: SLNA 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (V\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 mau ch\u00f3ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-tai-pho-nui-hlv-tai-em-to-hagl-duoc-trong-tai-thien-vi-168-189359.html\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ed1 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-168-189318.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3880","checkdouble":"189935"},{"date":"09:46 29/06","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao Real ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar gia nh\u1eadp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/29/tu-hao-chau-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Paris Saint-Germain.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Neymar</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian qua, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Neymar. Nh\u1eefng Karim Benzema, Gareth Bale \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00ea th\u1ea3m v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i bu\u1ed9c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar. Ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSG t\u1eeb Barcelona v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 m\u1eb7n m\u00e0. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p khi\u1ebfn anh c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dani Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dani Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/Dani-Carvajal-chao-don-Neymar-toi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Neymar t\u1eeb PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian Neymar tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Brazil d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Real \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p anh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, sau khi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil k\u1ebft th\u00fac World Cup 2018, ph\u00eda Real s\u1ebd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 350 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi PSG \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Carvajal mu\u1ed1n Neymar gia nh\u1eadp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDani Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real Madrid. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c CLB \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 si\u00eau sao 26 tu\u1ed5i. \u201cN\u1ebfu Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sinh ra \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Madrid, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Cadena SER.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar Carvajal\" title=\"Neymar Carvajal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/tu-hao-chau-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Carvajal ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Neymar t\u1edbi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMadrid lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. N\u1ebfu ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u00e9t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCarvajal \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Alvaro Odriozola, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Real Sociedad. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, anh c\u0169ng m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Odriozola \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9\u201d, Carvajal n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Odriozola l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.\u201d <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-real-sap-ban-ronaldo-180-189885.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Real s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/asensio-thua-nhan-kha-nang-roi-real-madrid-180-189770.html\">Asensio th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-rut-ruot-real-madrid-172-189735.html\">HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-sao-real-madrid-172-189650.html\">MU gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3879","checkdouble":"189932"},{"date":"09:08 29/06","title":"Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi sao s\u00e1ng World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/chelsea-tien-gan-toi-golovin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin \u2013 ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Nga \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow. M\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga. V\u00e0 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 2 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, Golovin \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0110T Nga. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb \u0111i b\u00f3ng, s\u00fat xa, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho t\u1edbi gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn m\u00ea m\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin sao s\u00e1ng World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin sao s\u00e1ng World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/chelsea-tien-gan-toi-golovin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin khi chi \u0111\u1eadm</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Juventus khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Golovin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Chelsea ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Golovin sau khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro (27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft gh\u1ebf HLV</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tuy nh\u00ean, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u00f3n Maurizio Sarri v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Napoli v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Antonio Conte.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea quy\u1ebft sa th\u1ea3i Conte m\u1eddi Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nConte v\u1eabn l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng cao khi \u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i CLB b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia. Trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua Golovin, Conte kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1edfi Granovskaia v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Roman Abramovich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Nga mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Alexey Smertin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Abramovich tin Golovin \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea-172-189734.html\">Hazard n\u00ean t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-voi-napoli-vi-hlv-sarri-172-189709.html\">Chelsea v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n &ldquo;chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; HLV Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-thang-7-172-189593.html\">Chelsea ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3878","checkdouble":"189928"},{"date":"10:14 29/06","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Wilshere","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/16/wilshere-sap-toi-fenerbahce-sau-khi-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jack Wilshere s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Fenerbahce ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Wilshere chia tay Arsenal</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJack Wilshere gia nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n Arsenal n\u0103m 2001 khi m\u1edbi 9 tu\u1ed5i. N\u0103m 2008, t\u1ee9c khi m\u1edbi 16 tu\u1ed5i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i 1 Ph\u00e1o v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Wilshere v\u1edbi Arsenal h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n sau khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 k\u1ebft th\u00fac. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, anh tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emirates. \u201cT\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal FC sau khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6\u201d, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Fenerbahce ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Fenerbahce ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/10/Jack-Wilshere-sap-toi-Fenerbahce-choi-bong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal khi kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a HLV\u00a0Emery</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau nhi\u1ec1u cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i CLB, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 HLV m\u1edbi Unai Emery, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ra \u0111i. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1eb1m trong v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 17 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Bolton v\u00e0 Bournemouth. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, t\u00e2n HLV Emery kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Wilshere l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere\" title=\"Wilshere\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/west-ham-chi-ky-hop-dong-voi-wilshere-neu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Wilshere s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Fenerbahce ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Arsenal, nghe \u0111\u00e2u Jack Wilshere s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Fenerbahce ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. Nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, Volkan Demir ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111ang \u1edf Istanbul \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFenerbahce c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nhi\u1ec1u CLB \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Wilshere. Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Istanbul, c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Galatasaray v\u00e0 Besiktas c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng n\u00e0y. T\u1ea1i Premier League, c\u00f3 West Ham li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Wilshere, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ng\u1eafn h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eddi Arsenal ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/santi-cazorla-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-toi-jack-wilshere-172-189052.html\">Santi Cazorla c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Jack Wilshere</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-muon-mua-dennis-praet-cua-sampdoria-172-187155.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Serie A thay Wilshere</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bi-loai-khoi-dt-anh-wilshere-trach-mang-hlv-southgate-172-186545.html\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Anh, Wilshere n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wilshere-se-chot-tuong-lai-sau-cuoc-gap-hlv-emery-172-188179.html\">Wilshere s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p HLV Emery</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3877","checkdouble":"189936"},{"date":"18:44 28/06","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/9/doi-tre-ha-noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-u19-viet-nam-du-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Doi-tre-Ha-Noi-ap-dao-doi-hinh-U19-Viet-Nam-du-giai-U19-Dong-Nam--hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Qu\u00e2n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfm s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 23 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110N\u00c1 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 10 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 D\u01b0\u01a1ng T\u00f9ng L\u00e2m, \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n T\u1edbi, Li\u1ec5u Quang Vinh, Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n Nam, B\u00f9i Ho\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Anh, Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n, L\u00ea V\u0103n Xu\u00e2n, Tr\u1ea7n V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, L\u00ea Xu\u00e2n T\u00fa v\u00e0 L\u00ea V\u0103n Nam.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb. Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB Viettel, B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p, PVF v\u00e0 HAGL.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a-168-189289.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i xem nh\u1eb9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, Narakorn Noomchansakul \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Duy Ki\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u00ea B\u00ecnh Minh, Tr\u1ea7n B\u1ea3o To\u00e0n, D\u1ee5ng Quang Nho. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd CLB SLNA kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o s\u1ea3n sinh ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danh sach U19 Viet Nam\" title=\"Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/36288595_219841762074064_4634375763716472832_n.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Danh s\u00e1ch U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0110N\u00c1</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3876","checkdouble":"189877"},{"date":"20:55 28/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Real s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ronaldo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/8/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-real-sap-ban-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, theo OK Diario, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Real Madrid gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Los Blancos l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1 t\u1ef7 euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/10/Day!-Dau-hieu-cho-thay-Cristiano-Ronaldo-roi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, vi\u1ec7c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi ra 1 t\u1ef7 euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua CR7 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Ronaldo c\u0169ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, theo OK Diario, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho MU v\u00e0 Man City</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">OK Diario kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m t\u1eeb 1 t\u1ef7 euro xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ronaldo real madrid\" title=\"ronaldo real madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/5/3/messi-cu-vo-tu-nang-ao-an-mung-con-nang-cup-hay-de-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chi ra 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, MU ho\u1eb7c Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, n\u1ebfu Los Blancos b\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y CR7 ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb OK Diario \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, v\u00e0 PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf La Liga, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n anh t\u1edbi PSG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo s\u1ebd thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 MU, Man City, AC Milan, Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf ra 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3875","checkdouble":"189885"},{"date":"18:54 28/06","title":"Burnley b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \"r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\" Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/21/burnley-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-liverpool.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Turf Moor ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1eeb 8 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Danny Ings\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Burnley, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Ings kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/21/burnley-bat-ngo-muon-rut-ruot-liverpool.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t cho Danny Ings</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Ings ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Roberto Firmino \u0111ang l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool, The Kop v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 sao tr\u1ebb Solanke v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sturridge, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanny Ings \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, The Kop c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Danny Ings</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Turf Moor ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra t\u1eeb 8 \u0111\u1ebfn 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua Danny Ings c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/20/danny-ings-thua-nhan-hoc-theo-firmino-de-lay-lai-phong-do-tot-nhat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Burnley mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Danny Ings</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Turf Moor tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Burnley, Danny Ings s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 7 tr\u00ean BXH gi\u1ea3i NHA m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Ings \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/david-moyes-len-ke-hoach-hut-mau-liverpool-172-173090.html\" target=\"_blank\">West Ham mua Danny Ings</span> nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, theo \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Ings v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 cao, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng n\u1ebfu tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Burnley.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3874","checkdouble":"189875"},{"date":"03:40 29/06","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Rooney x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/11/chinh-thuc-rooney-xac-nhan-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 MLS.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nRooney chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi x\u1ee9 c\u1edd hoa<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man United v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh &ndash; Wayne Rooney m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi DC United, sau khi ch\u1ed1t xong m\u1ecdi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 bay t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft CLB m\u1edbi, v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u00e3 Shrek s\u1ebd m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 14/7 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y &ndash; khi DC United ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Vancouver Whitecaps tr\u00ean SV\u0110 m\u1edbi Audi Field.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a M.U cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp DC United, v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00fa v\u1ecb trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u1edbi SV\u0110 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa s\u1ebd khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng. Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp MLS \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng tham v\u1ecdng s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Wayne Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United c\u1ee7a MLS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Wayne Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United c\u1ee7a MLS h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/CHINH-THUC-Wayne-Rooney-gia-nhap-DC-United-cua-MLS-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean kh\u00e1t khao gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p cho CLB 100% kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Khi t\u00f4i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a h\u00e8, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i CLB, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 SV\u0110 Audi Field.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n trong chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o m\u1edbi, thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho CLB n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Wayne Rooney kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng M\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Washington Post, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i, nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 13 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00eda Everton x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Rooney gia nh\u1eadp DC United, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 &ndash; ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ibrahimovic c\u1ee7a LA Galaxy.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rooney-o-dau-trong-ngoi-den-huyen-thoai-cua-man-united-172-163718.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/10/rooney-o-dau-trong-ngoi-den-huyen-thoai-cua-man-united.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/rooney-o-dau-trong-ngoi-den-huyen-thoai-cua-man-united-172-163718.html\">Rooney \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1n huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Man Utd?</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Wayne Rooney, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Everton. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-ban-rooney-bang-duoc-172-186716.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/everton-muon-ban-rooney-bang-duoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-ban-rooney-bang-duoc-172-186716.html\">Everton quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec5n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Rooney</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a, Everton mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Rooney sang gi\u1ea3i Nh\u00e0 ngh\u1ec1 M\u1ef9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Sam Allardyce, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3873","checkdouble":"189906"},{"date":"16:19 28/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng n\u1eef C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/nhung-nu-cdv-bong-da-quyen-ru-nhat-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"3872","checkdouble":"189852"},{"date":"16:46 28/06","title":"Sao H\u00e0n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f3 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/sao-han-tung-bung-mung-chien-thang-kho-tin-truoc-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Park Shin Hye, Hwang Seung Eun v\u1ee1 \u00f2a khi tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eafng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014. </h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Hinh-anh-sao-Han-mung-chien-thang-Han-Quoc-2-0-Duc-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129 Bae Ki Sung v\u00e0 b\u00e0 x\u00e3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat h\u1ed3i h\u1ed9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi khi theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ed1i 27/6. Tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, anh vi\u1ebft \"Win\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m vui chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Hwang-Seung-Eun-7841-1530156279.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Hwang Seung Eun tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \"c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c\". Hwang Seung Eun cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4 v\u1ee1 \u00f2a c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \"h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o, bi\u1ebft \u01a1n\" c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/haha-9199-1530156279.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <p class=\"Image\">Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean, ca s\u0129 Haha chia s\u1ebb h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 k\u00e8m bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng  \"b\u1eafn tim\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 sung s\u01b0\u1edbng\u00a0khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c d\u1eabn b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c. </p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/yoona-4258-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <p class=\"Image\">Yoona \u0103n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh to\u00e0n  \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.\u00a0C\u00f4 vi\u1ebft: \"C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\u00a0th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3  l\u00e0m h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh\". </p>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Untitled-5-9634-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ji Sook \u0111\u0103ng \u1ea3nh chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, k\u00e8m theo chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i \u0111ang kh\u00f3c\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/lee-su-bin-6850-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Lee Su Bin vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Instagram: \"G\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c anh l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/park-shin-hye-5037-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p Park Shin Hye vi\u1ebft: \"N\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u01a1i. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/jung-hae-in-2554-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0\"Trai \u0111\u1eb9p\" Jung Hae In: \"T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c anh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/sao-1-4115-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129 Jo Kwon: \"C\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 r\u1ed3i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/yoon-3791-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Yoon Kyun Sang: \"\"N\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 tu\u00f4n r\u01a1i. D\u00f9 cho c\u00e1c anh kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c - m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi - th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00fang ta chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0. T\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta. G\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 - c\u00e1c anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1edbn m\u1ea1nh n\u1eefa. K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u, quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u\".</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh sao H\u00e0n m\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2-0 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/Rain-7255-1530156280.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0Ca s\u0129, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Rain, \u00f4ng x\u00e3 c\u1ee7a Kim Tae Hee: \"Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. R\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o\". </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/phan-ung-trai-chieu-cua-cdv-duc-vs-han-quoc-sau-tran-cau-lich-su-461-189855.html\">Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a C\u0110V \u0110\u1ee9c vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuoi-dau-ruot-voi-hang-loat-anh-che-ve-that-bai-cua-dt-duc-421-189850.html\">C\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u1ea3nh ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/video-dt-duc-dong-goi-hanh-ly-len-duong-ve-nuoc-421-189848.html\">Video: \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-dan-anh-ha-he-sau-that-bai-e-che-cua-tuyen-duc-421-189839.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh h\u1ea3 h\u00ea sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u00ea ch\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/duc-nhuc-nha-roi-world-cup-ca-the-gioi-noi-gi-421-189837.html\">\u0110\u1ee9c cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi World Cup, c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tuyen-duc-bi-che-nhao-ra-sao-sau-khi-som-thanh-cuu-vuong-world-cup-421-189834.html\">Tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o ra sao sau khi s\u1edbm th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3871","checkdouble":"189857"},{"date":"16:08 28/06","title":"Martial, Morata v\u00e0 Icardi s\u1eafp s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nhau?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/28/martial-morata-va-icardi-sap-sat-canh-ben-canh-nhau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, Alvaro Morata, v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Tuttosport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mua 3 sao kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mua 3 sao kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/Chuyen-nhuong-Juventus-2018-mua-3-sao-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gonzalo Higuain \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGonzalo Higuain l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp thay th\u1ebf Conte mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nh\u1eafm Higuain thay Cavani.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaulo Dybala c\u0169ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Real v\u00e0 Liverpool l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca th\u00ec quan t\u00e2m Miralem Pjanic, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ra \u0111i, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus nh\u1eafm 3 sao l\u1edbn thay th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Tuttosport, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial, Alvaro Morata, v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 ba Higuain, Dybala v\u00e0 Pjanic.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/martial-morata-va-icardi-sap-sat-canh-ben-canh-nhau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus nh\u1eafm Morata v\u00e0 Martial n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Anthony Martial v\u00e0 Alvaro Morata l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Martial \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U th\u00ec Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Morata \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRi\u00eang tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Mauro Icardi th\u00ec kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n b\u1edfi Inter Milan mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan kh\u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean b\u00e1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong c\u00f9ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Emre Can theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3870","checkdouble":"189847"},{"date":"14:25 28/06","title":"HAGL m\u1ea5t C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 V-League v\u00ec \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a V-League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t.</h2><h2>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong HAGL vs Than Quang Ninh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/hagl-mat-cong-phuong-o-vong-17-vleague-vi-an-phat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn HAGL vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Ng\u1ecdc Ch\u00e2u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a HAGL do \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn 3 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng. \u00c1n ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Qu\u1ea3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc song h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Tam K\u1ef3. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 3 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 4.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 l\u1ea1i mang t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p cho HAGL, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m 3-2 t\u1ea1i c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018. Khi \u1ea5y C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap k\u00e8m th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi m\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c trong nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hagl-40-quang-ninh-dau-an-nguyen-van-toan-168-189697.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 4-0 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n</span><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 16 V-League 2016, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 xong m\u00f3n n\u1ee3 \u0111\u00e3 vay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh b\u1eb1ng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1eadm 4-0 t\u1ea1i Pleiku. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3869","checkdouble":"189842"},{"date":"15:14 28/06","title":"Atletico Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n \"h\u00fat m\u00e1u\" Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/atletico-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-hut-mau-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd quan t\u00e2m Cesar Azpilicueta\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAtletico Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau khi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Thomas Lemar c\u1ee7a Monaco, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/atletico-madrid-bat-ngo-muon-hut-mau-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Atletico h\u1ecfi mua Azpilicueta\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/dai-gia-la-liga-chinh-thuc-so-huu-thomas-lemar-voi-gia-khung-180-188349.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico mua Lemar th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. El Gol Digital \u0111\u01b0a tin, Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Cesar Azpilicueta c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. N\u1ebfu chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Atletico s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Cesar Azpilicueta</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Atletico mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Cesar Azpilicueta l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. El Gol Digital kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y kinh ph\u00ed chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Joao Miranda t\u1eeb Inter Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ESPN chi ra rang chi con Azpilicueta muon chien dau cho Antonio Conte.\" title=\"ESPN ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n Azpilicueta mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho Antonio Conte.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/Antonio-Conte-va-cuoc-chuyen-giao-chang-em-dep-tai-Etihad-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Azpilicueta \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu trung v\u1ec7, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y Azpilicueta \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Azpilicueta c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea t\u1eeb Marseille v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3868","checkdouble":"189844"}]}